108
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:36,401
...setelah Ibumu menyuruhmu
berhenti merokok.

109
00:25:38,360 --> 00:25:40,362
Ada Internet.

110
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:53,080
- Hanya salah satu zombi.
