176
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:56,485
- Daryl.
- Kau mau menembak?

177
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:58,608
- Aku tak tahu caranya.
- Ini mudah.

178
00:29:58,760 --> 00:30:00,285
